      <title>Bouncey returns - more canvas physics</title>
      <link>http://mwcz.org/blog/2011/11/17/bouncey-returns---more-canvas-physics</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Nov 2011 22:25:00 EST</pubDate>
